steps.instruction:
The calculation to assess the Mo-enzymes content was performed according to the formula taking into account the absorbance of the control solution at 548 nm. The Mo-enzymes content was expressed in Units. The calculation was performed in several steps. In the first step, the blank value was subtracted from the sample value of all samples used (Eq. 1).(1)X=ODsample−OD‾controlwhere X is the absorbance value, which is used to calculate the nitrite concentration; ODsample
- sample absorbance at 548 nm; OD‾control
- average value of the blank absorbance at 548 nm;
